{"tid":2329363,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】阿桑奇已正式要求川普總統赦免","createTime":"2020-12-17T07:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T01:52:03.000Z","uid":25468,"like":157,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3c321b9f66a6813dfbc1ffba497fcdcda3476c5f","tid":2329363,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/wp-content/uploads/Donald-Trump-Wikileaks-Julian-Assange-Nigel-Farage-Ecuador-Roger-Stone-Guccifer-2-0-600x348.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegatewaypundit.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FDonald-Trump-Wikileaks-Julian-Assange-Nigel-Farage-Ecuador-Roger-Stone-Guccifer-2-0-600x348.jpg&h=4a2203d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJulian Assange formally requested a pardon from President Donald Trump on Tuesday morning, the Gateway Pundit can now reveal.<br />\n<br />\nPeople from across the political spectrum have called on President Trump to pardon the WikiLeaks founder, citing the importance of the freedom to publish.<br />\n<br />\nAssange&rsquo;s fianc&eacute; Stella Morris, the mother of his two young children, has previously called for a pardon &mdash; but a formal request was not filed with the White House until this week.<br />\n<br />\nAssange is imprisoned in the United Kingdom pending a decision about his extradition to the United States where he faces charges under the Espionage Act for his publication of the Iraq and Afghan War Logs. If convicted he could face a maximum sentence of 175 years for the &ldquo;crime&rdquo; of publishing material that the US government did not want the population to know.<br />\n<br />\nIn 2018, President Trump&rsquo;s attorneys quietly made a case in defense of WikiLeaks throughout legal filings responding to a lawsuit filed by Democrat Party donors who alleged that the campaign and former advisor Roger Stone conspired with Russians to publish the leaked Democratic National Committee emails.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2020/12/julian-assange-formally-requested-pardon-president-donald-trump/?ff_source=Twitter&amp;ff_medium=PostTopSharingButtons&amp;ff_campaign=websitesharingbuttons\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegatewaypundit.com%2F2020%2F12%2Fjulian-assange-formally-requested-pardon-president-donald-trump%2F%3Fff_source%3DTwitter%26ff_medium%3DPostTopSharingButtons%26ff_campaign%3Dwebsitesharingbuttons&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28WINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=749844ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2020/12/julian-assange-formally-requested-pardon-president-donald-trump/?ff_source=Twitter&amp;ff_medium=PostTopSharingButtons&amp;ff_campaign=websitesharingbuttons</a>"},{"pid":"bb1956f09586fa85a81734d77f392e0e4d9b474d","tid":2329363,"uid":218313,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:57:13.000Z","msg":"唔係PARDON 左啦咩"},{"pid":"31fc6ed16c63cf007a1b5d91b411fee46dc31dd4","tid":2329363,"uid":26708,"like":162,"dislike":4,"score":158,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyKT1Qr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyKT1Qr.jpg&h=d57c3cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAre you ready"},{"pid":"5c1416f1c0bb1b1ad19654ed96945c831efb981e","tid":2329363,"uid":308915,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bb1956f09586fa85a81734d77f392e0e4d9b474d","tid":2329363,"uid":218313,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:57:13.000Z","msg":"唔係PARDON 左啦咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:02:38.000Z","msg":"嗰個係「傳」Trump準備Pardon"},{"pid":"c4fc9be53ed9ef86a08cdf6ea2efa6471380f5f1","tid":2329363,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb1956f09586fa85a81734d77f392e0e4d9b474d","tid":2329363,"uid":218313,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:57:13.000Z","msg":"唔係PARDON 左啦咩"},"citedBy"